cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

This paper is about natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on text augmentation techniques for low-resource languages. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper discusses image processing techniques, which could potentially place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves data manipulation, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses NLP techniques, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
